mytaxi gets you where you need to be – safely, quickly and easily.
Now when you enter your destination we will show you the estimated arrival time.
Please keep in mind that traffic and street conditions may vary on your actual journey.

Join millions of people across Europe, and experience the best in style and comfort with the mytaxi app!
Please leave us a review on the App Store – we love hearing your feedback!
For any questions please contact uk.support@mytaxi.com in the UK, or ireland.support@mytaxi.com in Ireland.

mytaxi gets you where you need to be – safely, quickly and easily.
Join millions of people across Europe, and experience the best in style and comfort with the mytaxi app!

You can now easily choose the mytaxi you need. Simply tap on Multi-Seater, Eco-Taxi, the small pet option or many more.
Look out for our upcoming discount campaigns: Our vouchers look more shiny now and you can handle them more easily.

For any questions please contact uk.support@mytaxi.com in the UK, or ireland.support@mytaxi.com in Ireland.

Our latest app update has a brand new display making it easy for you to choose the taxi you want. Decide between more seats, wheelchair-accessible alternatives, or simply book the nearest available taxi. Enter your destination first to check the price estimate before your trip. (Available services may vary depending on your location).

If you need help or if you have any suggestions, email us at help@mytaxi.com.

Plan ahead this year with the latest Prebook features:

YOUR BOOKINGS
Check your scheduled prebooks and go over the details of upcoming mytaxi trips.

ADD IT TO YOUR CALENDAR
Simply add new mytaxi Prebooks to the calendar on your device. Name your calendar entries, e.g. mytaxi Airport Transfer.

Got a question? Need assistance? Get in touch at uk.support@mytaxi.com in the UK, or ireland.support@mytaxi.com in Ireland.
